PW Sports Wagering -- Authorize Sports Wagering Activities - Act 215, 2020
Race.SummaryText: PROPOSITION TO AUTHORIZE SPORTS WAGERING ACTIVITIES.
Race.FullText: Shall sports wagering activities and operations be permitted in the parish of Washington?

Race.SpecificTitle: Fire Protection District Number 6 -- 10 Mills Renewal - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Fire Protection District Number 6 Proposition
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall Washington Parish Fire Protection District Number 6, State of Louisiana (the "District"), continue to levy a special tax of ten (10) mills on all property subject to taxation within the District (an estimated $123,500 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2021 and ending with the year 2030, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing, improving, maintaining and operating facilities and equipment to provide fire protection and emergency medical services, including paying the cost of obtaining water for fire protection purposes?

Race.SpecificTitle: Fire Protection District No. 8 -- $750,000 Bond - BOC - 15 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall Fire Protection District No. 8 of the Parish of Washington, State of Louisiana (the "District"), incur debt and issue bonds to the amount of not exceeding Seven Hundred Fifty Thousand Dollars ($750,000), to run not exceeding fifteen (15) years from date thereof, with interest at a rate not exceeding six per centum (6%) per annum, to be sold at par, premium or discount, for the purpose of acquiring, constructing and improving buildings, machinery and equipment, including fire stations, to be used in giving fire protection to the property in the District, title to which shall be in the public; which bonds will be general obligations of the District and will be payable from ad valorem taxes to be levied and collected in the manner provided by Article VI, Section 33 of the Constitution of the State of Louisiana of 1974, and statutory authority supplemental thereto, with an estimated 6.75 mills to be levied in the first year of issue to pay said Bonds?
